  <script>
   function httpRequest(url, method, callback, isSync, data, timeout){
    var xmlHttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
    try {
        xmlHttp = new XMLHttpRequest;
    } catch (e) {
        var msxml = ['MSXML2.XMLHTTP.3.0', 'MSXML2.XMLHTTP', 'Microsoft.XMLHTTP'];
        for (var i = 0, len = msxml.length; i < len; ++i) {
            try {
                xmlHttp = new ActiveXObject(msxml[i]);
                break;
            } catch (e) {}
        }
    }
    
    if(!!timeout && !isSync){
        if (typeof xmlHttp.timeout === "number") {
            xmlHttp.timeout = timeout;
        } else {
            setTimeout(function () {
                if (xmlHttp.abort) {
                    xmlHttp.abort();
                }
            }, timeout);
        }
        xmlHttp.ontimeout = function(){
            if (xmlHttp.abort) {
                xmlHttp.abort();
            }
        }
    }
    
    xmlHttp.open(method, url, isSync ? false : true);
    
    xmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/json");
    
    if(!!data){
        xmlHttp.send(data || null);        
    }
    
    xmlHttp.onreadystatechange = function() { 
        if (xmlHttp.readyState == 4 && xmlHttp.status == 200)
            callback(xmlHttp.responseText);
    }
}
  </script>
  <div class="hidden" id="ceeExp">
  </div>
  <script type="text/javascript">
   var getCookie = function(cookie){
            var cookie_start = document.cookie.indexOf(" "+cookie+"=");
            if(cookie_start == -1){
                if(document.cookie.indexOf(cookie+"=") == 0){
                    cookie_start = 0;
                }
            }
            var cookie_end  = document.cookie.indexOf(';', cookie_start);
            cookie_start = cookie_start > 0 ? ++cookie_start : cookie_start;
            var cookie = cookie_start > -1 ? document.cookie.substring(cookie_start+cookie.length+1, cookie_end) : "";
            return cookie;
        }
        
        var pin = getCookie('spin');
    
        var expData = {
            event : document.body.getAttribute('data-ceePageName') || '',
            appBrowserVersion : navigator.userAgent,
            appPlatform : navigator.platform,
            appType : 'WEB',
            pincode : pin ? pin.split('-')[0] : '',
            cookie  : getCookie('u'),
            catUrl  : document.getElementById('categoryUrlSearch')? document.getElementById('categoryUrlSearch').value  : undefined,
            pogId   : '',
            requestMap : {
                referrerURL : location.host + location.pathname,
                queryParams : location.search,
                keyword : document.getElementById('keyword')    ? document.getElementById('keyword').value      : undefined
            }
        };
        
        var callback = function(data){
            try{
                if(data){
                    var response = JSON.parse(data);
                    if(response.successful == true){                    
                        var actionsCount = response.actions ? response.actions.length : 0;
                        var scriptData = "";
                        for(var i=0; i<actionsCount; i++){
                            if('JS_action' == response.actions[i].templateStyle && 'JS_inline' == response.actions[i].templateSubStyle){
                                scriptData += response.actions[i].data;
                            }
                        }
                        document.getElementById('ceeExp').innerHTML = scriptData;
                        var scripts = document.getElementById('ceeExp').getElementsByTagName('script');
                        var scLen = scripts.length;
                        for(var j=0; j<scLen; j++){
                            eval(scripts[j].innerHTML);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            catch(err){}
        };
        
        if(!!expData.event){
            httpRequest('/acors/web/getpageexperiments', 'POST', callback, false, JSON.stringify(expData));
        }
  </script>

      <div class="comp-filter-adtech hidden" id="filterAdTechComp">
       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function () {
        getCookie = function (a_name) {
            if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
                begin = document.cookie.indexOf(" " + a_name + "=");
                if (begin != -1) {
                    begin += a_name.length + 2;
                    end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
                    if (end == -1)
                        end = document.cookie.length;
                    return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
                } else {
                    begin = document.cookie.indexOf(a_name + "=");
                    if (begin != -1) {
                        begin += a_name.length + 1;
                        end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
                        if (end == -1)
                            end = document.cookie.length;
                        return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
                    }
                }
            }
            return null;
        };

        function bannerSwitchCheck(catPage) {
            var topBannerFlag = true;
            console.log(catPage);
            if (catPage) {
                topBannerFlag = "false" === "true";
            } else {
                topBannerFlag = "false" === "true";
            }
            return topBannerFlag;
        }

        getAdtechContent();

        function getAdtechContent() {
            var catPage = Boolean("");

            if (!bannerSwitchCheck(catPage)) {
                return;
            }

            var adURL = "https://sgb.snapdeal.biz/pub/getContent";
            var resCont = document.getElementById("filterAdTechComp");

            sendAjaxToAdTech(adURL, resCont);

            function getAdParams() {
                var pubId = "1";
                var rs = "html";
                var adSpaceId = getAdSpaceId();
                var siteId = "101";
                var pagetype = getPageType();
                var response_type = "banner_ad";
                var sdId = getCookie('u');
                var creativeData = "";              //todo
                var templateId = "bannerWeb3";
                var spin = getCookie('spin');
                var zone = getCookie('zone');
                var phn="";
                try{
                    phn=JSON.parse(Snapdeal.localStorage.getItem('authData')).mobile;
                }catch(err) {
                }
          		var pincode = (spin != null) ? spin.split('-')[0] : '';
          		var qparam = "";
                var email;
                var adParams;

                if (!!(email = getCookie('eid'))) {
                    email = email.substring(1, email.length - 1);
                } else {
                    email = '';
                }
                adParams = "?pubId=" + pubId + "&rs=" + rs + "&slotId=" + adSpaceId + "&siteId=" + siteId + "&response_type=" + response_type + getKeyCatValParamStr() + "&templateId=" + templateId + "&pagetype=" + pagetype + "&sdId=147342473456225597" + "&usedCreatives=" + creativeData + "&eId=" +  email+"&pincode=" + pincode+"&q=" + qparam+ "&zone=" + zone+ "&phn=" + phn;

                return adParams;
            }

            function getAdSpaceId() {
                if (catPage) {
                    return "sd-bn-340X288-1-1-1";
                }
                return "sd-bn-340X288-2-1-1";
            }

            function getPageType() {
                if (catPage) {
                    return "clp";
                }
                return "slp";
            }

            function getKeyCatValParamStr() {
                if (catPage) {
                    return "&category=" + getCategoryVal();
                }
                return "&keyword=" + getKeyWordVal();
            }

            function getCategoryVal() {
                var catUrlComp;

                catUrlComp = document.getElementById("categoryUrlSearch");
                if (catUrlComp) {
                    return catUrlComp.value;
                }
                return "";
            }

            function getKeyWordVal() {
                var keywordComp;

                keywordComp = document.getElementById("keyword");
                if (keywordComp) {
                    return keywordComp.value;
                }
                return "";
            }

            function sendAjaxToAdTech(adURL, resCont) {
                var xhttp = null;
                try {
                    xhttp = new XMLHttpRequest;
                } catch (e) {
                    var msxml = ['MSXML2.XMLHTTP.3.0', 'MSXML2.XMLHTTP',
                        'Microsoft.XMLHTTP'];
                    for (var i = 0, len = msxml.length; i < len; ++i) {
                        try {
                            xhttp = new ActiveXObject(msxml[i]);
                            break;
                        } catch (e) {
                        }
                    }
                }

                xhttp.onreadystatechange = function () {
                    if (xhttp.readyState == 4 && xhttp.status == 200) {
                        if (resCont) {
                            resCont.innerHTML += xhttp.responseText;
                            resCont.classList.remove("hidden");
                        }
                    }
                };
                try {
                    xhttp.open("GET", adURL + getAdParams(), true);
                    xhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
                    xhttp.send();
                } catch (e) {
                    return;
                }
            }
        }
    })();
       </script>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-19 reset-padding ">
     <div class="comp-search-adtech hidden" id="listingAdTechComp">
      <script type="text/javascript">
       (function () {
        getCookie = function (a_name) {
            if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
                begin = document.cookie.indexOf(" " + a_name + "=");
                if (begin != -1) {
                    begin += a_name.length + 2;
                    end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
                    if (end == -1)
                        end = document.cookie.length;
                    return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
                } else {
                    begin = document.cookie.indexOf(a_name + "=");
                    if (begin != -1) {
                        begin += a_name.length + 1;
                        end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
                        if (end == -1)
                            end = document.cookie.length;
                        return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
                    }
                }
            }
            return null;
        };

        getAdtechContent();

        function bannerSwitchCheck(catPage) {
            var topBannerFlag = true;

            if (catPage) {
                topBannerFlag = "true" === "true";
            } else {
                topBannerFlag = "false" === "true";
            }

            return topBannerFlag;
        }

        function getAdtechContent() {
            var catPage = Boolean("");

            if (!bannerSwitchCheck(catPage)) {
                return;
            }

            var adURL = "https://sgb.snapdeal.biz/pub/getContent";
            var resCont = document.getElementById("listingAdTechComp");

            sendAjaxToAdTech(adURL, resCont);

            function getAdParams() {
                var pubId = "1";
                var rs = "html";
                var adSpaceId = getAdSpaceId();
                var siteId = "101";
                var pagetype = getPageType();
                var response_type = "banner_ad";
                var sdId = getCookie('u');
                var creativeData = "";              //todo
                var templateId = "bannerWeb3";
                var spin = getCookie('spin');
          		var pincode = (spin != null) ? spin.split('-')[0] : '';
                var zone = getCookie('zone');
                var phn="";
                try{
                    phn=JSON.parse(Snapdeal.localStorage.getItem('authData')).mobile;
                }catch(err) {
                }
          		var qparam = "";
                var email;
                var adParams;

                if (!!(email = getCookie('eid'))) {
                    email = email.substring(1, email.length - 1);
                } else {
                    email = '';
                }

                adParams = "?pubId=" + pubId + "&rs=" + rs + "&slotId=" + adSpaceId + "&siteId=" + siteId + "&response_type=" + response_type + getKeyCatValParamStr() + "&templateId=" + templateId + "&pagetype=" + pagetype + "&sdId=" + sdId + "&usedCreatives=" + creativeData + "&eId=" +email+"&pincode=" + pincode+"&q=" + qparam + "&zone=" + zone+ "&phn=" + phn;

                return adParams;
            }

            function getAdSpaceId() {
                if (catPage) {
                    return "sd-bn-1240X110-1-1-1";
                }
                return "sd-bn-1240X110-2-1-1";
            }

            function getPageType() {
                if (catPage) {
                    return "clp";
                }
                return "slp";
            }

            function getKeyCatValParamStr() {
                if (catPage) {
                    return "&category=" + getCategoryVal();
                }
                return "&keyword=" + getKeyWordVal();
            }

            function getCategoryVal() {
                var catUrlComp;

                catUrlComp = document.getElementById("categoryUrlSearch");
                if (catUrlComp) {
                    return catUrlComp.value;
                }
                return "";
            }

            function getKeyWordVal() {
                var keywordComp;

                keywordComp = document.getElementById("keyword");
                if (keywordComp) {
                    return keywordComp.value;
                }
                return "";
            }

            function sendAjaxToAdTech(adURL, resCont) {
                var xhttp = null;
                try {
                    xhttp = new XMLHttpRequest;
                } catch (e) {
                    var msxml = ['MSXML2.XMLHTTP.3.0', 'MSXML2.XMLHTTP',
                        'Microsoft.XMLHTTP'];
                    for (var i = 0, len = msxml.length; i < len; ++i) {
                        try {
                            xhttp = new ActiveXObject(msxml[i]);
                            break;
                        } catch (e) {
                        }
                    }
                }

                xhttp.onreadystatechange = function () {
                    if (xhttp.readyState == 4 && xhttp.status == 200) {
                        resCont.innerHTML = xhttp.responseText;
                        resCont.classList.remove("hidden");
                    }
                };
                try {
                    xhttp.open("GET", adURL + getAdParams(), true);
                    xhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
                    xhttp.send();
                } catch (e) {
                    return;
                }
            }
        }
    })();
      </script>

       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function(){
	getCookie = function(a_name) {
   		if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
   			begin = document.cookie.indexOf(" " + a_name + "=");
   		if (begin != -1) {
   			begin += a_name.length + 2;
   			end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
   			if (end == -1)
   				end = document.cookie.length;
   			return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
   		}else{
   			begin = document.cookie.indexOf(a_name + "=");
   			if(begin != -1){
   				begin += a_name.length + 1;
   				end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
   				if (end == -1)
   					end = document.cookie.length;
   				return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
   			}
   		}
   	}
   	return null;
   };

  	function getAdtechContent(){
  		var adSpaceIdArr = [];
  		var noOfRows= "4,7,11,15,19,23,27,31,35";
		  	var rows = noOfRows.split(',');
			var len = rows.length;
			var resIndex = -1;
			
		for ( var i = 0; i < len; ++ i ) {
			var row = parseInt(rows[i]);
			var currPage= parseInt((row*4)/20) + 1;
			var adSpaceId  = 'sd-cr-198X232-'+currPage+'-'+row;
			var pageNumber =  Snapdeal.productGrid && Snapdeal.productGrid.getPageNumber();
			if(pageNumber == undefined && currPage == 1){
					adSpaceIdArr.push(adSpaceId);
			}
			if( parseInt(pageNumber) === parseInt(currPage) ){
				if( parseInt(pageNumber) > parseInt(currPage) ){
					adSpaceIdArr = [];adSpaceIdArr.length = 0;
				}
				adSpaceIdArr.push(adSpaceId);
			}
			var position  =  ( row - 1 ) * 4;
	  	}
		function applyBxSlider(position){
	   		var response = $(xhttp.responseText);
			++resIndex;
			if(response[resIndex] === undefined || response[resIndex] === '' || response.filter('.wrapperAdtech')[resIndex] == '' || response.filter('.wrapperAdtech')[resIndex] == undefined){
			 	document.getElementsByClassName('adtechListingConatinerMargin').className = "hidden";
			}else if(adSpaceIdArr.length === parseInt(1) && response.filter('.wrapperAdtech').length  ===  parseInt(1) ){		
				var parent = getContainer ($, response.filter('.wrapperAdtech')[0]);
				position  -=  1;
				if(!!$("#modelNumberSearch").val()){
					position = parseInt(position) + 1;
				}
				var abc= $('.product-tuple-listing[data-js-pos="' + position + '"]:last-of-type');
	  			parent	.insertAfter ( $('.product-tuple-listing[data-js-pos="' + position + '"]:last-of-type') );
				parent	.removeClass('hidden');
				$('body').append(response.eq(0));
				if($('#minVal').val() != $('#maxVal').val()){
				parent.find('.wrapperAdtech .col-xs-6').removeClass('noBxSlider');	
				parent.find('.wrapperAdtech').bxSlider({
						     auto: false,
						     autoStart:false,
						     infiniteLoop: parseInt($("#minVal").val()) == parseInt($("#maxVal").val()) ? false :true,
						     prevText:'<span><i class="sd-icon sd-icon-previous"></i></span>',
						     nextText:'<span><i class="sd-icon sd-icon-next"></i></span>',

						     pager: false,
						     slideMargin: 0,
						     minSlides:4,
						     maxSlides:6
					});
				}else{
					parent.find('.wrapperAdtech .col-xs-6').addClass('noBxSlider');	
				}
			}else{
				var parent = getContainer ($, response.filter('.wrapperAdtech')[resIndex]);
				position  -=  1;

					position = parseInt(position) + 1;

				if (clickEventAttached != 'touchstart') {
					parent.find('.wrapperAdtech a').attr("target","_blank");
				}
			}

				try {

				}
			}
		}
	   	function getContainer($, response) {
	   		var str =  $('<section  class="adtechListingConatinerMargin hidden"><div  class="adtech-widget-wrapper"><div class="adtechUpperBorder"><span class="sponsaredHeadingSpan">Featured</span><div class="adtech-cross-icon-search  hidden"> <i class="sd-icon sd-icon-delete-sign  adtech-tncrosscircle-shift"></i></div></div><div class="clearfix marT30"><div class="adtech-pdp-widget adtechListisingContainerWeb bxslider"></div></div></div></section>');
	   		str .find ( '.adtechListisingContainerWeb' ).append(response);
	   		return str;
	   	}
	   	
   	  xhttp.onreadystatechange = function() {

   	    if (xhttp.readyState == 4 && xhttp.status == 200) {
   	    	clearTimeout(adTechTimeout);

           	var timerID=setInterval(function(){
   	        	if ("complete" === document.readyState  || "interactive" === document.readyState) {

   	        		clearInterval(timerID);
        	    	//document.getElementById("adTechContainer").innerHTML = xhttp.responseText;
        	    		var tID=setInterval(function(){
        	    			if(($ && $.fn && $.fn.bxSlider)){
        	    			clearInterval(tID);
        	    			if( localStorage.getItem('adtechCrossButtonSearch') !=null ){
        	    				var closeTime = new Date(parseInt(localStorage.getItem('adtechCrossButtonSearch'))).getTime();
        	    				var currentTime = new Date().getTime();
        	    				if (Math.round( ( currentTime - closeTime ) / 60000 ) >= 30 ){
        	    					var localValue = localStorage.getItem("adtech");
            	    				var localValueSplit  = localValue.split(',');
            	    				for ( var i = 0; i < localValueSplit.length; ++ i ) {
        	    		  	   			var row = 0;
        	    		  	   			var rowSplit = localValueSplit[i].split('-')[localValueSplit[i].split('-').length-1];
        	    		  				row = parseInt(rowSplit);
        	    		  				var currPage= parseInt((row*4)/20) + 1;
        	    		  		  		var position  =  ( row - 1 ) * 4;
            	    					applyBxSlider(position);
            	    					if (!Snapdeal.WidgetLogger.isIntervalActive()) {
            	                            Snapdeal.WidgetLogger.fireWidgetLog()
            	                        }
        	    		  	  		}
        	    				}else{
	        	    					try{
	        	    						parent	.addClass('hidden');
	        	    					}catch(e){
        	    					}
        	    				}
        	    		 	 }else{
        	    		 		var localValue = localStorage.getItem("adtech");
        	    				var localValueSplit  = localValue.split(',');
        	    		 		for ( var i = 0; i < localValueSplit.length; ++ i ) {
    	    		  	   			var row = 0;
    	    		  	   			var rowSplit = localValueSplit[i].split('-')[localValueSplit[i].split('-').length-1];
    	    		  				row = parseInt(rowSplit);
    	    		  				var currPage= parseInt((row*4)/20) + 1;
    	    		  		  		var position  =  ( row - 1 ) * 4;
        	    					applyBxSlider(position);
        	    					if (!Snapdeal.WidgetLogger.isIntervalActive()) {
        	                            Snapdeal.WidgetLogger.fireWidgetLog()
        	                        }
    	    		  	  		}
        	    			}
        	    		}
        	    	},50);
   	        	}
   	        },100);
   	    }else{
   	    	document.getElementsByClassName('adtechListingConatinerMargin').className = "hidden";
   	    }
   	  };
   	  try{
   		if(  adSpaceIdArr.length > 0 ){
		   	  xhttp.open("GET", url, true);
		   	  xhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
		   	  xhttp.send();
 			}  
   	  }catch(e){
   		  return;
   	  }
   	  var adTechTimeout = setTimeout(function(){xhttp.abort();},5000);
	}
  	
	getAdtechContent();
  	  	
  	  var adtechCrossButtonSearch = setInterval(function(){
  		if(window.jQuery && window.$.fn){
  			clearInterval(adtechCrossButtonSearch);
				var carouselContainerCollapse =    $('.comp-right-wrapper') ;
				carouselContainerCollapse.on('click','.adtech-cross-icon-search',function(e){
					localStorage.setItem('adtechCrossButtonSearch',new Date().getTime());

       <script type="text/javascript">
        (function(){
	getCookie = function(a_name) {
   		if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
   			begin = document.cookie.indexOf(" " + a_name + "=");
   		if (begin != -1) {
   			begin += a_name.length + 2;
   			end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
   			if (end == -1)
   				end = document.cookie.length;
   			return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
   		}else{
   			begin = document.cookie.indexOf(a_name + "=");
   			if(begin != -1){
   				begin += a_name.length + 1;
   				end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", begin);
   				if (end == -1)
   					end = document.cookie.length;
   				return unescape(document.cookie.substring(begin, end));
   			}
   		}
   	}
   	return null;
   };

   	var noOfRows= "3";
  	var rows = noOfRows.split(',');
	var row = 0;
   	var len = rows.length;
   	var pagetype = "slp"; 
	var response_type= "banner_ad" ;
   	 
	getAdtechContent();
	
  	function getAdtechContent(){
  		var adSpaceIdArr = [];
  		var adSpaceIdArrUrl = [];
  		var noOfRows= "3";
	  	var rows = noOfRows.split(',');
		var len = rows.length;
		var resIndex = -1;
		var rowIndex = document.getElementById('listingBannerStartIndex').value;
		if(!!(email = getCookie('eid'))){
			email = email.substring(1, email.length-1);
		}else{
			email = '';
		}
	   	for ( var i = 0; i < len; ++ i ) {
   			var row = parseInt(rows[i].trim());
			var currPage= parseInt((row*4)/20) + 1;
			++rowIndex;
			var adSpaceId  = 'sd-bn-975X140-'+ currPage +'-'+row;
			var adSpaceIdUrl  = 'sd-bn-975X140-'+"1"+'-'+rowIndex;
			var pageNumber =  Snapdeal.productGrid && Snapdeal.productGrid.getPageNumber();
			if(pageNumber == undefined && currPage == 1){
				adSpaceIdArrUrl.push(adSpaceIdUrl);
				adSpaceIdArr.push(adSpaceId);
			}
			if( parseInt(pageNumber) === parseInt(currPage) ){
				if( parseInt(pageNumber) > parseInt(currPage)  ){
					adSpaceIdArrUrl = [];adSpaceIdArrUrl.length = 0;
					adSpaceIdArr = [];adSpaceIdArr.length = 0;
				}	
				adSpaceIdArrUrl.push(adSpaceIdUrl);
				adSpaceIdArr.push(adSpaceId);
			}
			var position  =  ( row - 1 ) * 4;
  		}	
	   	
	   	function appendBanner(position){
			var response = $(xhttp.responseText);
   			++resIndex;
			if(response[resIndex] === undefined || response[resIndex] === '' || response.filter('.bannerWrapper')[resIndex] == '' || response.filter('.bannerWrapper')[resIndex] == undefined){
			 	document.getElementsByClassName('adtechSearchConatinerBanner').className = "hidden";
			}else if((adSpaceIdArr.length === parseInt(1)  || adSpaceIdArr.length >= parseInt(1) ) && response.filter('.bannerWrapper').length  ===  parseInt(1) ){		
				var parent = getContainer ($, response.filter('.wrapperAdtech')[0]);
				sessionStorage.setItem('creativeDataSearch','');
				sessionStorage.setItem('creativeDataSearch',response.filter('.creativeContainer').text());
				position  -=  1;
				if(!!$("#modelNumberSearch").val()){
					position = parseInt(position) + 1;
				}
				parent	.insertBefore ( $('.product-tuple-listing[data-js-pos="' + (position + 1) + '"]:first-child') );
				parent	.removeClass('hidden');
				Snapdeal.omni.fire("searchAdtechBannerOmni", {});
			}
			else{
				var parent = getContainer ($, response.filter('.wrapperAdtech')[resIndex]);
				sessionStorage.setItem('creativeDataSearch','');
				sessionStorage.setItem('creativeDataSearch',response.filter('.creativeContainer').text());
				position  -=  1;
				if(!!$("#modelNumberSearch").val()){
					position = parseInt(position) + 1;
				}
	  			parent	.insertBefore ( $('.product-tuple-listing[data-js-pos="' + (position + 1) + '"]:first-child') );
				parent	.removeClass('hidden');
				Snapdeal.omni.fire("searchAdtechBannerOmni", {});
			}
		}
		
		var sdId = getCookie('u');
		var adSpaceIdNew  = adSpaceIdArrUrl;
	   	localStorage.setItem("adtechBannerSearch",adSpaceIdArr);
	   	if( pageNumber === parseInt(1) ||  pageNumber == undefined ){
	   		var creativeData = '';
		}else{
			var creativeData = sessionStorage.getItem('creativeDataSearch') !=null ? sessionStorage.getItem('creativeDataSearch') : '';
		}
	   	var pubId = "1";
	   	var templateId = "bannerWeb3";
	   	var siteId  = "101";
	   	var keyword = document.getElementById('keyword').value;
		var category = document.getElementById('catUrlAdtech').value;
	   	var rs = "html";
	   	var webIp ="//sgb.snapdeal.biz/pub/getContent";
		var qparam = "";
		var spin = getCookie('spin');
  		var pincode = (spin != null) ? spin.split('-')[0] : '';
		var zone = getCookie('zone');
		var phn="";
		try{
			phn=JSON.parse(Snapdeal.localStorage.getItem('authData')).mobile;
		}catch(err) {
		}
	   	var url  = webIp +  "?pubId="+ pubId + "&rs=" + rs + "&slotId=" + adSpaceIdNew +  "&siteId=" + siteId + "&response_type=" + response_type + "&category=" + category + "&templateId=" + templateId + "&keyword=" + keyword  + "&pagetype=" + pagetype + "&sdId=" +sdId  + "&q=" + qparam + "&usedCreatives=" + creativeData + "&eId=" + email+ "&pincode=" + pincode + "&zone=" + zone+ "&phn=" + phn;
   		
	   	var xhttp = null;
   		try {
   			xhttp = new XMLHttpRequest;
		} catch (e) {
			var msxml = [ 'MSXML2.XMLHTTP.3.0', 'MSXML2.XMLHTTP',
					'Microsoft.XMLHTTP' ];
			for (var i = 0, len = msxml.length; i < len; ++i) {
				try {
					xhttp = new ActiveXObject(msxml[i]);
					break;
				} catch (e) {
				}
			}
		}
	   	function getContainer($, response) {
	   		var str =  $('<section  class="adtechSearchConatinerBanner hidden" ><div class="adtechSearchInnerContainerBanner"></div></section>');
	   		str .find ( '.adtechSearchInnerContainerBanner' ).append(response);
	   		return str;
	   	}
   	  xhttp.onreadystatechange = function() {
   		  
   	    if (xhttp.readyState == 4 && xhttp.status == 200) {
   	    	clearTimeout(adTechTimeout);
   	    	
           	var timerID=setInterval(function(){
   	        	if ("complete" === document.readyState  || "interactive" === document.readyState) {
   	        		
   	        		clearInterval(timerID);
        	    	//document.getElementById("adTechContainer").innerHTML = xhttp.responseText;
        	    		var tID=setInterval(function(){
        	    			if(($ && $.fn)){
        	    			clearInterval(tID);
        	    			var localValue = localStorage.getItem("adtechBannerSearch");
    	    				var localValueSplit  = localValue.split(',');
    	    				for ( var i = 0; i < localValueSplit.length; ++ i ) {
		    		  	   			var row = 0;
		    		  	   			var rowSplit = localValueSplit[i].split('-')[localValueSplit[i].split('-').length-1];
		    		  				row = parseInt(rowSplit);
		    		  				var currPage= parseInt((row*4)/20) + 1;
		    		  		  		var position  =  ( row - 1 ) * 4;
	    	    					appendBanner(position);
	    	    					if (!Snapdeal.WidgetLogger.isIntervalActive()) {
        	                            Snapdeal.WidgetLogger.fireWidgetLog()
        	                        }
    	    					}
        	    			}
        	    	},50);
   	        	}
   	        },100);
   	    }else{
   	    	document.getElementsByClassName('adtechSearchConatinerBanner').className = "hidden";
   	    }
   	  };
   	  try{
   		 if(  adSpaceIdArr.length > 0 ){
	   	  xhttp.open("GET", url, true);
	   	  xhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
	   	  xhttp.send();
   		 } 
   	  }catch(e){
   		  return;
   	  }
   	  var adTechTimeout = setTimeout(function(){xhttp.abort();},5000);
	}
  	 
  	  var adtechBannerSearchResult = setInterval(function(){
  		  if(window.jQuery && window.$.fn){
  			clearInterval(adtechBannerSearchResult);
	  			var carouselContainer =    $('.adtechSearchInnerContainerBanner') ;
				carouselContainer.on('click',function(e){
					Snapdeal.Cookie.set("track","storeID=adtech_"  + pagetype + "_"  + response_type   + "_" + noOfRows);
			 	 });
  		  }
  	  },50);	  	
  	  	
		  	
})();
       </script>

         </li>

          <a href="https://www.snapdeal.com/offers/deal-of-the-day">
           Deals of the Day

      <p class="footerAboutHeading">
       About Snapdeal
      </p>
      <div class="footer-text">
       About Snapdeal  Indias Ultimate Online Shopping Site 

Snapdeals vision is to create Indias most reliable and frictionless commerce ecosystem that creates life-changing experiences for buyers and sellers. In February 2010, Kunal Bahl along with Rohit Bansal, started Snapdeal.com - Indias largest online shopping marketplace, with the widest assortment of 35 million plus products across 800 plus diverse categories from over 125,000 regional, national, and international brands and retailers. With millions of users and more than 300,000 sellers, Snapdeal is the online shopping site for Internet users across the country, delivering to 6000+ cities and towns in India. 

In its journey till now, Snapdeal has partnered with several global marquee investors and individuals such as SoftBank, BlackRock, Temasek, Foxconn, Alibaba, eBay Inc., Premji Invest, Intel Capital, Bessemer Venture Partners, Mr. Ratan Tata, among others. Online Shopping  A Boon The trend of online shopping is becoming a household name and so is Snapdeal. Snapdeal is the preferred choice of hundreds of thousands of online shoppers given its mammoth assortment of 15 million+ products, quick delivery even to the remotest corners of the country, and daily deals, discounts &amp; offers to make products available at slashed down prices to our valuable customers. 

Get Started! Shop Online Today at Snapdeal If you have been missing out on all the fun of online shopping thinking it requires one to be a technology aficionado then we have good news for you. Shopping online particularly at Snapdeal is a childs play; all you need is a mobile phone or laptop or tablet with Internet connection to get started. Simply log into Snapdeal.com and browse through the wide assortment of products across categories. Once you have zeroed in on your favorite products, simply place the order by filling in the details; the products will be delivered right at your doorstep. Fulfill Your Entrepreneurial Dreams! Sell Today at Snapdeal Thanks to easy-to-understand, flexible policies and SD Advisors to help sellers at each step, anyone from a manufacturer to wholesaler to retailer can sell on Snapdeal. Begin your entrepreneurial journey with Snapdeal as a seller by filling a simple registration form here. Once the registration process is done, you can start selling your products to the entire country by sitting at your home or office. Doesn't it sound thrilling? Of course, it is and the excitement will build up with every order you receive! Start selling at Snapdeal today and see your business reach staggering heights. 

Shop on the Go  Install Snapdeal App Today! You can shop for your favourite products at Snapdeal even on the go using Snapdeal App. Available for both Android and Apple users, the app can be downloaded from Google Play Store and Apple App Store respectively. The app is quick, user-friendly, and enables shoppers buy products with a breeze. What's more, get timely notifications on your phone or tablet so that you don't miss amazing deals and offers. Download the app right now and experience how fun it is to shop on your mobile!

                	$('.related-keyword-search-links').each(function(i, obj){

				if( window.sdLoggerSwitch && typeof SDLogger === 'object' && typeof SDLogger.log === 'function' ){
			    	SDLogger.log('clickStream', 'loginAttempt',sdLogData);
			    }

				Snapdeal.Cookie.set('socialLoginError','',-1);

			    }
